{"tid":459312,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"（求教）1月冬天究竟去邊好","createTime":"2017-11-05T15:52:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T14:51:44.000Z","uid":51200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7fafc9e7493f5c9d36eb1a8d143f0e5c1835ee9d","tid":459312,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T15:52:33.000Z","msg":"小弟12月20去哈爾濱睇雪，<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n30號係長春完哂行程，<br />\n因為係參加U既交流活動，<br />\n所以淨係俾香港來回程交通費就得。<br />\n<br />\n不過小弟想玩耐d，畢竟1月十幾號先開學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家擬定幾條路線由長春出發，<br />\n無話玩幾日<br />\n玩完返香港，<br />\n唔知大家點睇呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBudget 10K(假設 機票來回長春+頭十日交流團洗費+保險 =4K，淨6k)<br />\n<br />\n1）長春去 長白山，打完個白鴿轉返長春，<br />\n之後返香港<br />\n<br />\n2) 長春去北京，再坐火車去南京返香港<br />\n<br />\n3) 長春去丹東，去北韓，再返丹東返香港<br />\n<br />\n4）大家有無其他意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e08594aed9926d895a2e1e27f24b565c2780352e","tid":459312,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T02:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4bd2dbbcac5d126db042b4ed222316ecc2ca4cb","tid":459312,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T06:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b02850b555f76ffc905b7941504fcfbfb3016dd","tid":459312,"uid":15348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T06:41:54.000Z","msg":"北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ae08078a6f3cd364bbb9035c0b61f15314e881","tid":459312,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T07:29:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a1db30366bf41054053fdc40835a23faf7ec94","tid":459312,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T10:47:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bf4c532e2c99e60abc6e7daf3a2d01e83f75bdc","tid":459312,"uid":55923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T10:52:39.000Z","msg":"海參威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd371f5aab4367d24de6cc5a565758bdb814e69e","tid":459312,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T15:20:23.000Z","msg":"北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06524f1f037e98920c295e22fdc12590be91456a","tid":459312,"uid":80624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T14:51:44.000Z","msg":"巴打咁岩<br />\n我同你情況一樣<br />\n不過1/1係上海完<br />\n諗住之後再去玩<br />\n可能會北京<br />\n有無興趣一齊去玩"}]}